   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CONTENTS Being Apt to Teach and Holding the Mystery How to Discuss the Matters of the Church How to Lead the Newly Saved Ones How to Receive the Saved Ones Two Matters Concerning Service A Few Questions Concerning Revelation and Religion The Altar of God</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>This book is composed of messages given in Chinese by Brother Witness Lee in Taipei, Taiwan in 1951.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Its seven chapters elucidate the true meaning of being apt to teach and of holding the mystery of the faith.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>They also cover a few matters concerning service, such as how to discuss church affairs, how to care for the newly saved ones, and how to receive the believers.</S>
